. * -------------------------------------------------------
. * HAUSMAN TEST: FE vs RE
. * -------------------------------------------------------

. estimates store fe_result
. xtreg lnOutput lnLabor lnCapital Leverage lnWage lnSize HHI, re
. estimates store re_result
. hausman fe_result re_result

                  ---- Coefficients ----
              |         (b)           (B)          (b-B)  sqrt(diag(V_b-V_B))
              |   fe_result     re_result     Difference                 S.E.
--------------+------------------------------------------------------------
       lnLabor|   0.4932683     0.6087704     -0.1155021            0.0341882
     lnCapital|   0.0481325     0.0367333      0.0113992            0.0162493
      Leverage|  -0.0000203     0.0438326     -0.0438529            0.0335486
        lnWage|   0.3623343     0.4319210     -0.0695868            0.0262857
        lnSize|   0.2854791     0.4154588     -0.1299797            0.0383893
           HHI|  -0.0010224    -0.0014581      0.0004357            0.0002784
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

            b = consistent under Ho and Ha; obtained from xtreg
            B = inconsistent under Ha, efficient under Ho; obtained from xtreg

Test:  Ho:  difference in coefficients not systematic

                chi2(6) = (b-B)'[(V_b-V_B)^(-1)](b-B)
                        =      83.87
            Prob>chi2 =      0.0000

  => Reject Ho: Use FIXED EFFECTS model  ***

